title: Seeking Her, Knowing You
description: Get ready for a journey. Author and dating coach Jess Branas takes you from point A to point B. With motivating women to understand themselves and focus on what they truly desire from a partner, Jess enables women to navigate the lesbian dating world with ease.The path begins with you. Through exploring the whole you, the roadmap to your success in dating is created. Through each detailed exercise, you will learn the steps it takes to become confident and decisive. You will learn what women really think, what attracts them and what they want by understanding your own mind.Finally, Jess offers an easy-to-follow 8 step breakdown for approaching and dating the women you desire.
author: Jess Branas
